Due to technical reasons car routing data provided separately. And in a more wide regions for better cross border routing.

File [issue](https://github.com/develar/gh-routing-data/issues) if routing data not provided for wanted country or region.

!!! warning "Experimental usage only"

    Latest available GraphHopper Add-on [doesn't support fully](https://github.com/graphhopper/graphhopper/issues/1401).
